      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. Power is managed by a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers. Mechanically, this M3 is superlative: rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance, and the valve clearances were recently shimmed to factory specifications. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior leather shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
